### Grid

- Use a **12-column grid** for page-level layout
- Gutter width: `{{spacing.baseUnit}}px` × 4 = {{multiply spacing.baseUnit 4}}px
- Maximum content width: 1280px
- Side margins collapse to `{{spacing.componentPadding.md}}` on mobile
